Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=============OP=========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:17.70,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直注视着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:24.29,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:31.26,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久很久 我一直将你的后背
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:35.43,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作我的依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:42.56,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来将自己身处的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:49.15,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作是临时的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:52.74,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避着 逃避着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:55.66,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃向梦想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.37,0:01:00.91,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抱住你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.75,0:01:04.87,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:07.79,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与想象中相反的单纯内里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:10.75,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都让那稚嫩的自我意识
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.72,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阵阵刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:22.18,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 拖着泥泞沉重的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:27.44,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过至少身体强悍 所以今天也微笑面对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:17.70,SonglmOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no usirosugata wo
